    Where Greek Tradition Meets Modern Elegance

    At Meli Estiatorio, we reimagine Greek dining with a modern, upscale touch. From freshly grilled seafood to signature cocktails, every detail is designed for elegance and experience. Located in Forest Hills, Queens, our restaurant is a destination for refined Mediterranean cuisine.

    ABOUT US

    Seasonal Seafood

    Sourced with care and grilled to perfection, our whole fish and seafood dishes bring the flavors of the Aegean coast to Forest Hills.

    Curated Wines

    Our wine list highlights both Greek varietals and global favorites, thoughtfully selected to complement every dish and elevate your dining experience.

    Elegant Mezze.

    Shareable small plates, from creamy spreads to crisp salads, invite guests to savor the heart of Greek hospitality in an elevated way.

    Book Your Table in Forest Hills

    Whether it’s an intimate dinner, a night with friends, or a celebration, Meli Estiatorio delivers upscale dining with personalized service. Secure your spot in our elegant dining room today.

    Events & Experiences at Meli

    Stay connected with our latest happenings—from live music and holiday specials to curated wine dinners. Every visit offers something new to experience in Forest Hills.

    Celebrate the Art of Sharing

    From vibrant mezze plates to fresh seafood pasta, every dish is crafted to slow you down and draw you into the moment. In Greece, Food is never rushed; it’s about laughter around the table, passing plates between friends, and raising a glass to life’s everyday joys.
